Get the Most from Your Tool Storage

Every home improvement project is easier when your tools are organized. Keep your tools neat and secure with a storage solution from The Home Depot. 

Mobile Workbenches Make Work Easier

A mobile workbench is a great addition to any garage or work space. Youll never be held to working in one spot again with a rolling workbench. Store your tools in your mobile workbench drawers for an easy storage solution. We carry mobile workbenches in small, medium and large sizes. Whether you need a toolbox for accessories, a tool chest for larger tools sets, a truck box for hauling equipment, or a workbench for your garage, when everything has its own place you save yourself time and headaches looking for the tools you need.

Take Your Work With You

Interlocking tool storage systems let you take your work on the road. The strong, interconnecting unit locks individual compartments in place, making it a breeze to organize your tools and accessories for easy transport. With an interlocking tool storage system, your days of losing tools are over. Need help deciding which storage system works best? Use our modular storage system buying guide to help you decide.

All Things Tool Storage

From tool bags and tool belts to tool chest combos and cabinets in every size, The Home Depot has what you need to protect your tools. When youre working on an involved DIY project, our heavy duty tool belt bags, give you more room for larger items. The knife holder belts keep your cutting tools safe and secure. Durable and highly functional utility pouches offer protective covers and easy access to hand tools, while drawer dividers help compartmentalize toolboxes for efficient use.
Our tool storage selection will help you save space, keep organized and get your project completed with ease.

Stay Organized

Keeping a neat workspace is a DIYer necessity. Why not make every area look as great as it works? Black tool boxes compliment home and work areas with sleek design. When your new DIY action puts you on the move, our guide for the Best Tool Belts, Bags and Pouches for Your Home Projects helps you keep everything you need close at hand. For even more ideas on how to make your home, work and decor flow seamlessly, check out our Workbench Ideas. Go from the bench to wall when you see How to Organize Tools on a Pegboard. The possibilities for new function and style are endless.

Tool Storage 46 in. W x 18 in. D 9-Drawer Mobile Workbench Cabinet in Gloss Black

The all new Husky 46 in. W x 18 in. D 9-Drawer Mobile Workbench Cabinet has arrived. This workbench has a 21-Gauge steel frame finished with a gloss black powder coat finish. There is a solid wood top that provides a 833 sq. in. work surface. On the right hand side is an integrated power strip providing 6 outlets and 2 USB ports to power and charge tools and batteries. Each of the drawers comes with a pre-cut liner and is supported by soft-closing ball-bearing slides that support up to 100 lbs. The deeper bottom drawers have a second set of slides to support heavier and bulkier items. A tubular side handle allows 1 to bring the workbench to wherever it is needed. 5 in. x 2 in. casters have a total load capacity of up to 1500 lbs.

Tool Storage 52 in. W Heavy Duty Matte Gray Tool Chest Combo

The latest generation of the Husky Industrial 52 in. W x 20 in. D 15-Drawer Tool Chest has arrived. The chest is built to last with all-welded 19-Gauge steel construction and is finished with a tough, industrial textured gray powder-coat finish. All drawers are full-extension and glide on ball bearing slides that can support up to 120 lbs. These slides also have a soft-close retention system that pulls drawers closed and ensures that they are secured. An additional set of slides has been added to the full-width drawer and bottom deep drawers to accommodate heavier loads. The reinforced top lid is supported by gas struts, which make it easier to open and close, while the back of the top till has a large magnetic plate that provides storage and quick access to frequently used tools. Also, inside the lid are 6 electrical outlets and 2 USB ports that allow you to securely charge tools and portable devices while unit is locked. The casters have been upgraded to an even heavier-duty 6 in. x 2 in. size and moving the cabinet around your workplace is easy with the ergonomic tubular handle.

PACKOUT 22 in. Rolling Modular Tool Box Low Profile Handle

The PACKOUT modular storage system is the industry's most durable and versatile storage system. The PACKOUT rolling tool box is constructed with impact resistant polymers and metal reinforced corners so it can withstand harsh jobsite environments. The rolling tool storage box connects with all other PACKOUT system components via integrated locking cleats and features a 250 lbs. of weight capacity. An industrial-grade extension handle and 9 in. all-terrain wheels ensure the tool box can be rolled anywhere on the jobsite. An IP65 rated weather seal protects tools and accessories from Rain and other jobsite debris. Interior organizer trays allow users to keep equipment organized to fit their needs. Reinforced hinges and carry handle ensure the rolling tool box is easily transportable wherever it is needed. The PACKOUT modular storage allows users to customize and build their own storage system to easily transport and organize tools and accessories.
